**Overall Meaning:**

Whose mind is placed within itself, having correctly known and given up what is to be rejected and accepted, his life shines.

This verse highlights the importance of self-awareness and discernment in living a meaningful life. It describes someone who has gained clarity about what truly matters and has let go of distractions and attachments. By focusing their mind inward and cultivating inner peace, they live a life that is radiant and fulfilling. 
